metadata.shopMessage:
**Browse the Gallery** and find Icon Packs, Wallpapers and Widgy Widgets by the best creators out there!

Filter what you want to see and open the preview to see more detail. Download direct to your iPhone or iPad.
metadata.shortcutsMessage:
**Explore** the Show shortcuts below. ShowLive & ShowLive Helper shortcuts are required to install themes with this app. Install and setup ShowLive first before downloading themes.

Shortcut versions are for **iOS 15.5 and higher**. See our Discord server for other versions.
metadata.howToMessage:
**Follow our tutorials** and learn how to select, download and apply themes with ShowLive. We cover everything to get you started with easy to follow videos and detailed step by step written instructions.

For further support visit our Discord server. Link at the bottom of this page.
metadata.themeDownloadInstructionsMessage:
#Once download completes:

The iOS share sheet will appear. Tap on **ShowLive Helper** to install the theme.

You can then choose to run the ShowLive shortcut to apply the theme on your device, or choose exit if you plan to apply the theme later
metadata.iconDownloadInstructionsMessage:
#ICON THEMES FOR YOUR HOMESCREEN

Icon Packs can be applied to your device by using the Apple Shortcuts app. **ShowLive DOES NOT theme your homescreen Icons!** See our Tutorials section for more details.

The image below only shows a sample of the complete icon pack for preview purposes.
metadata.wallpaperDownloadInstructionsMessage:
#WALLPAPERS FOR YOUR iPHONE

Tap on the image to view fullscreen. Download the full resolution wallpaper by tapping on the GET button.
metadata.widgyDownloadInstructionsMessage:
#WIDGY WIGETS FOR THE WIDGY APP

Tap on the image to view fullscreen. Download the Widgy Widget by tapping on the GET button.
